Interface Policy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PolicyTypes, Service
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PolicyStub

    public interface Policy
extends Service, PolicyTypes
    The Policy interface provides methods to manage local user accounts. This interface was added in vSphere API 6.7.
